sub_title: Product Manager at AOC / MMD Monitors & Displays
summary:
Hello! I am a Product & Business Manager with an analytical, entrepreneurial and team-player mindset. I have experience in different industries (IT, Professional AV and Consumer Electronics) and B2C and B2B sales channels.

Based in Amsterdam, I lead the product and business development of AOC and PHILIPS gaming products in Europe with outstanding sales, marketing and R&D teams!

Previously, I had great working experiences:
- In companies such as Procter & Gamble, HP, Samsung, and NGOs.
- Wide range of roles as Product and Business Development, Sales, Business Intelligence and Finance.
- Local and regional assignments in Latin America and Europe.
